              "text": "ASEAN Joint Statement on Climate Change to the 29th Session of the Conference of the Parties to the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC COP 29)",
              "link": "https://asean.org/asean-joint-statement-on-climate-change-to-the-29th-session-of-the-conference-of-the-parties-to-the-united-nations-framework-convention-on-climate-change-unfccc-cop-29/",
              "date": "October 12, 2024",
              "styles": ["bold", "underline"]
            }
          ]
        },
