              "date": "October 10, 2024",
              "styles": ["bold", "underline"],
              "content": "Dr. Kao Kim Hourn, Secretary-General of ASEAN, led the ASEAN Secretariat's delegation at the summits in Vientiane, Lao PDR. His participation underscores the Secretariat's role in facilitating regional cooperation and implementing ASEAN initiatives."
            },
            {
              "text": "Secretary-General of ASEAN Meets with the U.S. Ambassador to the United Nations",
              "link": "https://asean.org/secretary-general-of-asean-meets-with-the-u-s-ambassador-to-the-united-nations/",
              "date": "October 11, 2024",
              "styles": ["bold", "underline"],
              "content": "Dr. Kao Kim Hourn engaged in discussions with the U.S. delegation led by Ambassador Linda Thomas-Greenfield. The meeting focused on strengthening ASEAN-U.S. relations and exploring collaborative efforts in addressing regional and global challenges."
            },
